# SOPS Public Key for GitOps Infrastructure Control Plane
# This file contains the public age key for team collaboration
# Team members can use this key to encrypt new secrets

# Public key (replace with your actual public key after running setup-sops-keys.sh)
age1xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Instructions for team members:
# 1. Import this key: age-keygen -i .sops.pub.age
# 2. Use sops to encrypt new secrets with the shared configuration
# 3. Never share the private key - it should only exist in the cluster
